Bodoh.

00:01:21.873 --> 00:01:22.832
Dah tenang?

00:01:25.585 --> 00:01:26.669
Tak nak jawab?

00:01:27.253 --> 00:01:29.005
Apa yang kau nak?

00:01:29.589 --> 00:01:32.425
